==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water power
<hw>Wa"ter pow"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>The power of water
employed to move machinery, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A fall of water which may be used to drive
machinery; a site for a water mill; a water privilege.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water pox</ent>⟦br⟧
